Interface EntityResponse<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the entity type
All Superinterfaces:
ServerResponse
public interface EntityResponse<T> extends ServerResponse
Entity-specific subtype of ServerResponse that exposes entity data.
Since:
5.0
Author:
Arjen Poutsma, Juergen Hoeller
